#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Accounting &amp; Payments</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Contabilidad y pagos</strong>:"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Accounting</strong>: Easily generate tax reports and other financial "
"documents thanks to our localization packages."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Contabilidad:</strong> Genera reportes fiscales y otros documentos "
"financieros con facilidad gracias a nuestros paquetes de localización."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Add Images &amp; Categorization</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Agrega imágenes y categorías</strong>:"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>CRM</strong>: Manages customer relationships, tracks leads and "
"inquiries, and boosts sales potential."
msgstr ""
"<strong>CRM</strong>: Gestiona las relaciones con los clientes, rastrea los "
"leads y las consultas, y aumenta tus ventas."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Contacts</strong>: Organizes and stores client information for "
"personalized follow-ups."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Contactos</strong>: Organiza y almacena la información del cliente "
"para darle seguimiento personalizado."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Create a Product</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Crea un producto</strong>:"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Create a Purchase Order</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Crea una orden de compra</strong>:"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Email &amp; Social Marketing</strong>: Promote upcoming exhibitions "
"and special sales across different platforms"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Marketing por correo y redes sociales</strong>: Promociona las "
"próximas exposiciones y ventas especiales en distintas plataformas"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Events</strong>: Organize art exhibitions, artist meet-ups, and "
"gallery openings."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Eventos</strong>: Organiza exposiciones de arte, encuentros de "
"artistas y aperturas de galerías."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Extending the Workflow with Studio</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Flujos de trabajo más elaborados conStudio</strong>"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Manage Online Visibility</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Gestiona la visibilidad en línea</strong>:"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Manage your agreements 📝</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Gestiona tus contratos 📝</strong>"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Managing Commissions  👩‍🎨</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Gestiona tus comisiones 👩‍🎨</strong>"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Marketing Automation</strong>: Engage potential buyers with "
"personalized campaigns and newsletters."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Automatización de marketing</strong>: Interactua con los compradores "
"potenciales a través de campañas y boletines personalizados."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Memberships &amp; Subscriptions</strong>: Offer exclusive content, "
"VIP access, and limited-event participation."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Membresias y suscripciones</strong>: Ofrece contenido exclusivo, "
"acceso VIP y participación en eventos limitados."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.ir_ui_view_3577
msgid ""
"<strong>My Gallery</strong>\n"
"                      <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Mi Galería</strong>\n"
"                      <br/>"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>POS</strong>: Enables fast, in-store transactions for walk-in "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Punto de venta</strong>: Realiza transacciones con rapidez en la "
"tienda para atender clientes sin previa cita."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Projects</strong>: Manage large-scale exhibitions or arts festivals, "
"integrating planning, tasks, and team collaboration."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Proyectos</strong>: Gestiona exposiciones grandes o festivales de "
"arte. Integra tu planificación y tareas para colaborar en equipo."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Publish the Artwork</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Publica las obras de arte</strong>:"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Purchase</strong>: Helps manage vendor relationships and streamline "
"procurement processes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Compras</strong>: Gestiona las relaciones con los proveedores y "
"agiliza tus procesos de abastecimiento."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Receive the Artwork</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Recibe las obras de arte</strong>:"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Sales</strong>: Validates orders, creates custom quotations, and "
"streamlines the sales process."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ventas</strong>: Valida las órdenes, crea cotizaciones "
"personalizadas y agiliza el proceso de ventas."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Track New Artwork Opportunities</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Monitorea las oportunidades de las obras de arte</strong>:"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.ir_ui_view_1680
msgid "<strong>We are MyGallery.</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Somos MiGalería.</strong>"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Website &amp; eCommerce</strong>: Your gallery’s online storefront, "
"where customers can browse and purchase artworks anytime, anywhere."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Sitio web y Comercio electrónico</strong>: Crea una tienda en línea "
"para tu galería. Tus clientes podrán visitarla y comprar obras de arte en "
"cualquier momento desde cualquier lugar."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A potential buyer has inquired about an artwork—how exciting! Let’s go "
"through the steps to turn this inquiry into a sale."
msgstr ""
"¡Qué emoción! Un comprador potencial preguntó por una obra de arte. Veamos "
"qué pasos necesitarías para convertir esta consulta en una venta."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Accept various payment methods, including cash, credit cards, and mobile "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Acepta varios métodos de pago, por ejemplo, efectivo, tarjetas de crédito y "
"pagos desde el celular."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Acquiring new pieces for your gallery is seamless with <strong>CRM</strong> "
"and the <strong>Purchase App</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Usa las aplicaciones <strong>CRM</strong> y <strong>Compras</strong> para "
"adquirir obras nuevas para tu galería con facilidad."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add detailed product pages with high-resolution images, descriptions, and "
"pricing."
msgstr ""
"Agrega detalladas páginas de productos e incluye imágenes de alta "
"resolución, descripciones y precios."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add tags to your contacts to make it easy to sort between Artists and "
"Customers"
msgstr ""
"Agrega etiquetas a tus contactos para puedas ordenar artistas y clientes sin "
"complicaciones."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add the artwork as a product, specifying quantity, price, and expected "
"delivery date."
msgstr ""
"Agrega la obra de arte como un producto. Especifica su cantidad, precio y "
"fecha de entrega prevista."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adding Artwork to Your Collection 🎨"
msgstr "Agrega obras de arte a tu colección 🎨"

